cs.NE, cs.ET, cs.CV, cs.EM, cs.AR 

The paper discusses the use of memristive networks for swarm intelligence algorithms and image edge detection. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves hardware implementation, which suggests the category cs.ET (Emerging Technologies). The use of image processing techniques indicates the category cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of memristive devices, which suggests the categories cs.EM (Emerging Technologies) and cs.AR (Hardware Architecture).
